metadata.name: Kevin's Graduating Class of 2022 #1
metadata.description: The latest rendition of the Pixelmon saga. 6969 randomly-generated, photogenic Kevins wearing their best outfits and posing for the photo of the year. They've studied hard, trained to overcome their flaws, and have come to enlighten the bear market before Pixelmon's second coming. Congratulations to Kevin's Grad Class of 2022.
